title: Que times today.
body:
Jesus christ mary on a cross. 30 minutes+ for a game already and i'm still waiting.

I know this is after a patch and all but wow this is insane. I'm in bronze for this account atm and even then its impossible to find a game. I am not even queing up for positions hard to get either. 

Is there something wrong with the que atm??

replies.body: Tell me about it... 15 mins and counting for me.
